{"title":"数字三角形","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1220","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span>如图所示的数字三角形，从顶部出发，在每一结点可以选择向左走或得向右走，一直走到底层，要求找出一条路径，使路径上的值最大。</span></p>\n\n<img src=\"/source/codevs/codevs-1220/img/aHR0cDovL2NvZGV2cy5jbi9tZWRpYS9pbWFnZS9wcm9ibGVtLzEyMjAuZ2lm.gif\" style=\"max-width:700px\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行是数塔层数N(1&lt;=N&lt;=100)。</p>\n<p>第二行起，按数塔图形，有一个或多个的整数，表示该层节点的值，共有N行。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出最大值。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>5 </span></p>\n<p><span>13 </span></p>\n<p><span>11 8 </span></p>\n<p><span>12 7 </span>26</p>\n<p>6 14 15 8</p>\n<p>12 7 13 24 11</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>86</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n数字三角形\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}